More about summarize and grouping



df |&gt;
  group_by(C1, C2) |&gt;
  summarise(mean_3 = mean(C3)) |&gt;
  summarise(mean_again = mean(mean_3))

`summarise()` has grouped output by 'C1'. You can override using the
`.groups` argument.


